            <abstract id="ref3" label="Abstract">Charles Solomon was a socialist, a New York State Assemblyman, and a New York City magistrate. Contains correspondence, legal papers relating to matters brought before Solomon as magistrate, manuscripts, clippings and scrapbooks.</abstract>
            <physloc id="ref136" label="Location note">Materials are located at the Tamiment Library.</physloc>
            <langmaterial id="ref64" label="Language of Materials note">Materials are in English</langmaterial>
